  <SkipAbductionPlayerCompleteText>{INVOKER_nameDef}完成了{RITUAL_definite}仪式。通过操控时空，{INVOKER_nameDef}将来自{FACTION_name}派系的{TARGET_nameDef}拐了过来。仪式的骇人内幕让{TARGET_nameDef}陷入暂时昏迷之中。</SkipAbductionPlayerCompleteText>

