  <!-- Void awakening -->
  <!-- EN: Dimming sky -->
  <VoidAwakeningStageOneStructuresActivatedLabel>昏暗的天空</VoidAwakeningStageOneStructuresActivatedLabel>
  <!-- EN: Structures activated -->
  <VoidAwakeningStageTwoStructuresActivatedLabel>结构已激活</VoidAwakeningStageTwoStructuresActivatedLabel>
  <!-- EN: As the second structure is activated, the darkness begins to intensify. An unnatural darkness will soon descend. Make sure your colony is prepared. Stockpile resources, build lights, craft disruptor flares, and reinforce defenses. Only those in the light will be safe.\n\nMore twisted structures will appear soon. -->
  <VoidAwakeningStageOneStructuresActivatedText>随着第二座结构被激活，黑暗愈发浓烈。一片异常的黑暗很快就会将这里笼罩。确保你的殖民地有所准备。储备物资，建造光源，制作眩光背包，加固防御。只有在光亮下才是安全的。\n\n更多的扭曲结构马上就要出现了。</VoidAwakeningStageOneStructuresActivatedText>
  <!-- EN: All void structures have been activated. The space around the void monolith has begun to shimmer. Get ready. -->
  <VoidAwakeningStageTwoStructuresActivatedText>所有虚空结构都被激活了。虚空巨石周围的空间开始忽闪忽烁。做好准备吧。</VoidAwakeningStageTwoStructuresActivatedText> 
  <!-- EN: {STUDIER_nameDef} teleported -->
  <VoidAwakeningFinalStructuresActivatedLabel>{STUDIER_nameDef}遭到传送</VoidAwakeningFinalStructuresActivatedLabel> 
  <!-- EN: {STUDIER_nameDef} has activated the monolith and been ripped from our spacetime into another place.\n\n{STUDIER_pronoun} finds {STUDIER_objective}self in a room of jagged metallic spikes. Every surface is slick with dark fluid and the air vibrates with power. This metal hell is a connecting channel to an inhuman hyperintelligence. -->
  <VoidAwakeningFinalStructuresActivatedText>{STUDIER_nameDef}激活了巨石并掉出我们所在的时空，去往了另个空间。\n\n{STUDIER_pronoun}发现自己身处一座布满锯齿金属钉刺的房间里。每处表面都沾黏着深色液体，空气中振颤着能量。这座金属地狱便是连接那个非人超凡智能的通道。\n\n{STUDIER_nameDef}发现了能将梦魇心灵之力连向我们这个世界的虚空节点。与它互动，拥抱其中的力量；或者摧毁它，将连接彻底切断。</VoidAwakeningFinalStructuresActivatedText> 
  <!-- EN: Shambler assault -->
  <VoidAwakeningShamblerArrivalLabel>活尸袭击</VoidAwakeningShamblerArrivalLabel>
  <!-- EN: A horde of shamblers have been attracted by the void structures. Get ready! -->
  <VoidAwakeningShamblerArrivalText>一大群活尸被虚空结构吸引来了！做好准备！</VoidAwakeningShamblerArrivalText>
  <!-- EN: Fleshbeast tunneling -->
  <VoidAwakeningFleshbeastBurrowLabel>血肉兽隧掘袭击</VoidAwakeningFleshbeastBurrowLabel>
  <!-- EN: The monolith has generated a powerful psychic pulse, attracting nearby entities.\n\nBeneath the ground, you can hear meaty shrieks and scratching claws. Fleshbeasts are tunneling towards you. Get ready! -->
  <VoidAwakeningFleshbeastBurrowText>巨石产生了一道强力的心灵脉冲，吸引了附近的实体。\n\n肉耸的尖叫声连同利爪挖掘的声音从地下传来。一群血肉兽正在挖掘隧道向你袭来。做好准备！</VoidAwakeningFleshbeastBurrowText>
  <!-- EN: Metalhorror attack -->
  <VoidAwakeningMetalhorrorArrivalLabel>金属怪形袭击</VoidAwakeningMetalhorrorArrivalLabel>
  <!-- EN: Metalhorrors are appearing near the void monolith. Get ready! -->
  <VoidAwakeningMetalhorrorArrivalText>金属怪形正在从虚空巨石附近出现。做好准备！</VoidAwakeningMetalhorrorArrivalText>
  <!-- EN: Entity attack -->
  <VoidAwakeningEntityArrivalLabel>实体袭击</VoidAwakeningEntityArrivalLabel> 
  <!-- EN: The activated void structure has generated a twisted psychic pulse, attracting nearby entities. Get ready! -->
  <VoidAwakeningEntityArrivalText>激活的虚空巨石产生了一道扭曲的心灵脉冲，吸引了附近的实体。做好准备！</VoidAwakeningEntityArrivalText>
  <!-- EN: Embrace the void -->
  <VoidAwakeningBreadcrumbLetterLabel>拥抱虚空</VoidAwakeningBreadcrumbLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While interacting with the void structure, {PAWN_nameDef} saw a vision of the void. For a moment {PAWN_pronoun} swam the black ocean of infinite depth and felt its endless inhuman power.\n\n{PAWN_nameDef} thinks there may be a way to control that power by embracing the void. If you were to permanently open the conduit to the void, rather than shutting it down, it could offer untold possibilities. -->
  <VoidAwakeningBreadcrumbLetterText>在和虚空结构交互过程中，{PAWN_nameDef}看到了虚空的景象。{PAWN_pronoun}短暂地在那无尽的黑色海洋中遨游，感受着它那无穷的非人力量。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}认为可以通过接受虚空来找到控制那些力量的方法。如果你永久敞开这连通虚空的隧道，而不是将其关闭，将会带来无法预见的可能性。</VoidAwakeningBreadcrumbLetterText>

  <!-- Void node -->
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} returns -->
  <VoidNodeReturnedLabel>{PAWN_nameDef}回来了</VoidNodeReturnedLabel>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has reappeared. -->
  <VoidNodeReturnedMessage>{PAWN_nameDef}重新出现了。</VoidNodeReturnedMessage>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has reappeared.\n\n{PAWN_pronoun} looks withered by the inhuman thought-patterns of the void. All traces of humanity have left {PAWN_possessive} eyes.\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}'s mind and body are now permanently linked to the dark void of inhuman rage. Powered by this new connection, {PAWN_nameDef} no longer feels tethered to mortal needs like comfort or sleep. {PAWN_pronoun} has gained the ability to induce terror in others using the power of the void.\n\nThe monolith is awakened. It hums louder with {PAWN_nameDef}'s reappearance, a reminder that its connection to the void has been opened and made permanent. -->
  <EmbracedVoidText>{PAWN_nameDef}重新出现了。\n\n{PAWN_pronoun}似乎被那虚空里的非人思维模式搞得有些憔悴。{PAWN_possessive}眼中已经全无人性的痕迹。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}的身心如今与那充满非人狂热的黑暗虚空连接起来。{PAWN_nameDef}被此连接赋能，不再为凡人的需求所束缚，如进食和休息。凭借虚空的力量，{PAWN_pronoun}得到了催生恐惧的能力。\n\n巨石已经苏醒。它随着{PAWN_nameDef}的出现嗡鸣得愈发响亮，昭示着那连通虚空的大门已经永久打开。</EmbracedVoidText>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has reappeared. {PAWN_pronoun} is weary from {PAWN_possessive} efforts, but otherwise healthy.\n\nBy closing the channel to the void, {PAWN_nameDef} has stopped any more unnatural phenomena from entering our world. Hostile entities in the area have all fallen to the ground, lifeless.\n\nTales of {PAWN_possessive} heroism are sure to spread far and wide. -->
  <DisruptedLinkText>{PAWN_nameDef}重新出现了。{PAWN_pronoun}显然由于自己的努力落得有些疲惫，然而除此之外都挺健康。\n\n关闭虚空的通道后，{PAWN_nameDef}让任何异常事物再也无法进入我们的世界。当前区域内的敌对实体全都倒在地上，了无生气。\n\n{PAWN_possessive}英雄神话定会传唱千里、百世流芳。</DisruptedLinkText>
  <!-- EN: fleshcrafting -->
  <RewardFleshcraftingAbility>血肉铸造</RewardFleshcraftingAbility>
  <!-- EN: slaughter -->
  <RewardSlaughterAbility>宰杀</RewardSlaughterAbility>
  <!-- EN: shambler control -->
  <RewardShamblerControlAbility>控制活尸</RewardShamblerControlAbility>

  <!-- Duplicate sickness -->
  <!-- EN: Duplicate sickness -->
  <DuplicateSicknessLabel>复制后遗症</DuplicateSicknessLabel>
  <!-- EN: Both {0_nameDef} and {0_possessive} duplicate are feeling unwell. Their condition seems to be related to the duplication process and is worsening. The psychic connection that binds them is causing them to slowly lose consciousness. The condition won't get better until one of them dies. -->
  <DuplicateSicknessText>{0_nameDef}与{0_possessive}复制体都觉得有些不舒服。这番状况似乎是与复制过程有关，并且正在恶化。绑定着二者的心灵链接使两人都缓慢丧失着意识。情况在其中一人死亡前不会好转。</DuplicateSicknessText>

  <!-- Frenzied animals -->
  <!-- EN: Frenzied animals -->
  <FrenziedAnimalsLabel>发狂的动物</FrenziedAnimalsLabel>
  <!-- EN: A pack of man-hunting {0} have entered the area! They've been attracted by your ritual. They will roam the region hunting for humanoid flesh.\n\nThey won't attack doors unless they see someone go through the door. Hide inside and you'll be safe. They also won't attack powered-off turrets, so turn your turrets off to save them.\n\nThe {0} will leave the area in one or two days. You can hide and wait them out or fight them. -->
  <FrenziedAnimalsText>一群猎杀人类的{0}已经进入该地区。它们被你的仪式吸引而来，将四处游荡猎杀人类。\n\n它们不会攻击门，除非看见有人从门里穿过。因此最好还是把门关好，老实搁屋里呆着。它们也不会攻击关闭的炮塔，所以如果你想保住炮塔，可以考虑给炮塔断电。\n\n{0}将会在一两天内离开。你可以躲起来，或者出去跟它们战斗。</FrenziedAnimalsText>

  <!-- Ghouls -->
  <!-- EN: Ghoul betrayal -->
  <GhoulBetrayalLabel>食尸鬼背叛</GhoulBetrayalLabel>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has been driven mad by {PAWN_possessive} ravenous hunger for raw meat! -->
  <GhoulBetrayalText>{PAWN_nameDef}在对新鲜生肉的狂热饥饿下陷入了疯狂！</GhoulBetrayalText>
  
  <!-- Distress signal -->
  <!-- EN: Distress signal -->
  <DistressSignalLabel>求救信号</DistressSignalLabel>
  <!-- EN: You've intercepted a distress signal from a nearby camp of {FACTION_name}.\n\nThe frantic voice begs for immediate assistance defending against a threat. They offer everything at their camp in return for help, including shards of powerful archotechnology.\n\nAs the voice tries to explain the nature of the threat, the signal goes dead. -->
  <DistressSignalText>你接收到一个来自附近{FACTION_name}的营地传来的求救信号。\n\n对面的人用近乎狂乱的声音恳求着救援，希望有人来帮他们抵御威胁。他们愿意拿出营地里的一切作为回报，包括强力的暗黑超凡碎片。\n\n还没等对方讲清楚是什么威胁，信号就中断了。</DistressSignalText>
  <!-- EN: Ambush -->
  <DistressSignalAmbushLabel>伏击</DistressSignalAmbushLabel>
  <!-- EN: Fleshbeasts are emerging from a nearby pit burrow! -->
  <DistressSignalAmbushText>血肉兽正在从一处附近的深坑地洞里冒出来！</DistressSignalAmbushText>

  <!-- Chimeras -->
  <!-- EN: Chimeras approach -->
  <ChimeraAssaultLabel>嵌合兽接近</ChimeraAssaultLabel>
  <!-- EN: A group of twisted animal-like chimera monsters have appeared nearby.\n\nThe misshapen beasts will watch your colony, waiting for an opportunity to attack. They are skittish and may retaliate if provoked. -->
  <ChimeraAssaultText>一群扭曲的动物模样嵌合兽出现在了附近。\n\n这群畸形的野兽将会盯着你的殖民地，静待进攻的时机。当心了，它们受到挑衅后可能会发起报复。</ChimeraAssaultText>

  <!-- Unnatural darkness -->
  <!-- EN: Darkness lifting -->
  <DarknessLiftingEarlyLetterLabel>黑暗散去</DarknessLiftingEarlyLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: The last of the nightmarish pillars has collapsed. The unnatural darkness has begun to dissipate. Colonists breathe a sigh of relief in the clear air. -->
  <DarknessLiftingEarlyLetterText>随着最后一座梦魇之柱的倒塌。异常的黑暗开始散去。殖民者们终于可以呼吸到清新的空气了。</DarknessLiftingEarlyLetterText>
  <!-- EN: {0_nameDef} attacked -->
  <PawnAttackedInDarknessLabel>{0_nameDef}被攻击了</PawnAttackedInDarknessLabel>
  <!-- EN: Something in the darkness has attacked {0_nameDef}!\n\nThese attacks will continue until {0_pronoun} is safely in the light. -->
  <PawnAttackedInDarknessText>黑暗中有什么东西攻击了{0_nameDef}！\n\n在{0_pronoun}跑到光亮安全处前，这些攻击不会消停。</PawnAttackedInDarknessText>
  <!-- EN: Noctol attack -->
  <NoctolAttackLetterLabel>夜魇进攻</NoctolAttackLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: The darkness has begun to stir. Inhuman chittering sounds emerge from somewhere within the inky black.\n\nBlack, insect-like noctols will attack from the darkness soon. -->
  <NoctolAttackLetterText>黑暗开始翻腾起来。从那墨染的深黑中传来了非人之物的鸣叫声。\n\n那些虫子般的黑色夜魇很快就会从黑暗里攻过来了。</NoctolAttackLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Darkness soon -->
  <DarknessWarningLetterLabel>黑暗将至</DarknessWarningLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: The darkness is almost here. Only those in direct light from lamps, torches, or flares will be safe.\n\nTo keep colonists in the light, you can restrict their movement in the SCHEDULE tab by assigning allowed areas. -->
  <DarknessWarningLetterText>黑暗即将来临。只有那些光照充足的地方才是安全的，落地灯，火把，还有眩光照明弹都行。\n\n让殖民者们都待在光照充足的区域里，你可在“管制”标签页里设置活动区限制来限制他们不要乱跑。</DarknessWarningLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Darkness wavering -->
  <DarknessWaveringLetterLabel>黑暗减退</DarknessWaveringLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: With the destruction of the noctolith, a faint crack appears in the darkness, before being filled with more of the sooty black.\n\nDestroy the remaining noctoliths to end the unnatural darkness. -->
  <DarknessWaveringLetterText>随着夜光柱的毁灭，黑暗中出现了一丝裂痕，而这很快就会被更多的黑暗补上。\n\n毁灭剩余的夜光柱，将这异常的黑暗终结吧。</DarknessWaveringLetterText>

  <!-- Shambler Swarms -->
  <!-- EN: Shamblers approach -->
  <LetterLabelShamblerSwarmArrived>活尸猎群接近</LetterLabelShamblerSwarmArrived>
  <!-- EN: Shambler approaches -->
  <LetterLabelShamblerArrived>活尸接近</LetterLabelShamblerArrived>
  <!-- EN: A group of {0} shambling, rotting corpses is approaching. Some inhuman force has reanimated these lifeless bodies and set them to murder.\n\nThey will now wander through the area. If they see a human, they will attack. If not, they will leave in a few days.\n\nIf you can capture one, you can study it for anomaly knowledge. -->
  <LetterShamblerSwarmArrived>{0}只蹒跚而行的腐烂活尸正在接近。某种异常力量使这些早已失去生机的尸体重获行动能力。\n\n它们会在这片区域四处游荡，并攻击看到的人类。若能小心避开，它们几天后便会离去。\n\n如果你能捕获一只，可对其展开调查以获取异象研究知识。</LetterShamblerSwarmArrived>
  <!-- EN: A shambling, rotting corpse is approaching. Some inhuman force has reanimated this lifeless body and set it to murder.\n\nIt will now wander through the area. If it sees a human, it will attack. If not, it will leave in a few days.\n\nIf you can capture it, you can study it for anomaly knowledge. -->
  <LetterShamblerArrived>一只蹒跚而行的腐烂活尸正在接近。某种异常力量使这早已失去生机的尸体重获行动能力。\n\n它会在这片区域四处游荡，并攻击看到的人类。若能小心避开，它们几天后便会离去。\n\n如果你能捕获它，可对其展开调查以获取异象研究知识。</LetterShamblerArrived>
  <!-- EN: {ANIMALKIND_label} shamblers -->
  <LetterLabelShamblerAnimalsArrived>{ANIMALKIND_label}活尸</LetterLabelShamblerAnimalsArrived>
  <!-- EN: A group of shambling, rotting {ANIMALKIND_label} corpses is approaching. Some inhuman force has reanimated these lifeless bodies and set them to murder.\n\nThey will now wander through the area. If they see a human, they will attack. If not, they will leave in a few days.\n\nIf you can capture one, you can study it for anomaly knowledge. -->
  <LetterShamblerAnimalsArrived>一群蹒跚而行的腐烂{ANIMALKIND_label}活尸正在接近。某种异常力量使这些早已失去生机的尸体重获行动能力。\n\n它们会在这片区域四处游荡，并攻击看到的人类。若能小心避开，它们几天后便会离去。\n\n如果你能捕获一只，可对其展开调查以获取异象研究知识。</LetterShamblerAnimalsArrived>

  <!-- Ghoul pod crash -->
  <!-- EN: Transport pod crash -->
  <GhoulPodCrashLabel>运输舱坠毁</GhoulPodCrashLabel>
  <!-- EN: A transport pod carrying a ravenous hostile ghoul has landed nearby.\n\nThe ghoul is currently in shock, but it will soon recover and attack anyone it sees. It can be captured to a holding platform for further study.\n\nCapture or kill it before it wakes. -->
  <GhoulPodCrashText>一个装有凶恶敌对食尸鬼的运输舱坠毁在了附近。\n\n这只食尸鬼目前正处于心灵冲击状态，但很快就能恢复过来，然后攻击任何看到的人。可将其捕获至一座收容平台内以供后续研究。\n\n最好趁它醒来前将其捕获或杀死。</GhoulPodCrashText>
  <!-- EN: A transport pod carrying a ravenous hostile ghoul has landed nearby. On closer inspection, it appears to be {PAWN_nameDef}, a previous member of your crew.\n\nThe ghoul is currently in shock, but it will soon recover and attack anyone it sees. It can be captured to a holding platform for further study.\n\nCapture or kill it before it wakes. -->
  <GhoulPodCrashStartingPawnText>一个装有凶恶敌对食尸鬼的运输舱坠毁在了附近。经过近距离检查才发现，它竟是{PAWN_nameDef}，你们曾经的同伴。\n\n这只食尸鬼目前正处于心灵冲击状态，但很快就能恢复过来，然后攻击任何看到的人。可将其捕获至一座收容平台内以供后续研究。\n\n最好趁它醒来前将其捕获或杀死。</GhoulPodCrashStartingPawnText>

  <!-- Entity codex -->
  <!-- EN: New research available -->
  <LetterLabelEntityDiscovery>有新的可研究项目</LetterLabelEntityDiscovery>
  <!-- EN: Your discovery of {ENTITY_definite} has yielded new insights. You can now research the following Anomaly projects -->
  <LetterTextEntityDiscoveryResearch>通过对{ENTITY_definite}的发现你获得了新的见解。你现在可以进行以下异象研究项目</LetterTextEntityDiscoveryResearch>

  <!-- Nociosphere -->
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere defeated -->
  <NociosphereDefeatedLabel>已击败苦痛之球</NociosphereDefeatedLabel>
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere has been destroyed, leaving behind a number of valuable resources. -->
  <NociosphereDefeatedText>苦痛之球被摧毁了，留下一些有价值的资源。</NociosphereDefeatedText>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere destabilising -->
  <NociosphereBecomingUnstableLabel>苦痛之球失稳</NociosphereBecomingUnstableLabel> 
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere’s energy pattern has begun to shift and adapt. Within 10 days, it will no longer respond to suppression.\n\nThe nociosphere will activate if not suppressed. -->
  <NociosphereBecomingUnstableText>苦痛之球的能量模式已经开始调整并适应。10 天之内，它将不再对抑制有所反应。\n\n若不对其进行抑制，苦痛之球将会激活。</NociosphereBecomingUnstableText> 
  <!-- EN: Dispose of the nociosphere by sending it to attack a large hostile force. Once its onslaught is complete, it will permanently depart. -->
  <NociosphereBecomingUnstableTextExtraSendable>将苦痛之球送去攻击敌对派系以放逐它。待它杀个够以后，便会永久离开。</NociosphereBecomingUnstableTextExtraSendable>
  <!-- EN: Study the nociosphere to find a way to dispose of it. -->
  <NociosphereBecomingUnstableTextExtraNotSendable>调查苦痛之球以找到处置它的方法。</NociosphereBecomingUnstableTextExtraNotSendable>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere unstable -->
  <NociosphereUnstableLabel>苦痛之球不稳定</NociosphereUnstableLabel>
