  <NociosphereUnstableText>苦痛之球变得不稳定了，它不再对抑制有所反应。待其活跃度达到100%，它便会苏醒。</NociosphereUnstableText>
  <!-- EN: Dispose of the nociosphere by sending it to attack a large hostile force. Once its onslaught is complete, it will permanently depart. -->
  <NociosphereUnstableTextExtraSendable>将苦痛之球送去攻击敌对派系以放逐它。待它杀个够以后，便会永久离开。</NociosphereUnstableTextExtraSendable> 
  <!-- EN: Prepare for the nociosphere’s onslaught. -->
  <NociosphereUnstableTextExtraNotSendable>为苦痛之球的攻击做好准备吧。</NociosphereUnstableTextExtraNotSendable>

  <!-- EN: Strange corpse -->
  <UnnaturalCorpseArrivalLabel>诡异尸体</UnnaturalCorpseArrivalLabel>
  <!-- EN: An unnatural human corpse has appeared, as if out of thin air.\n\nOn further inspection, the corpse looks identical to {PAWN_nameDef}. Its skin feels waxy and warm to the touch.\n\nStudy the corpse to learn more about it. -->
  <UnnaturalCorpseArrivalText>一具不寻常的人类尸体似乎就这么凭空出现了。\n\n进一步检查发现，尸体与{PAWN_nameDef}简直一模一样。它的皮肤摸起来蜡润而温暖。\n\n研究这具尸体以了解更多信息。</UnnaturalCorpseArrivalText>

  <!-- EN: Golden cube -->
  <GoldenCubeArrivalLabel>金色魔方</GoldenCubeArrivalLabel>
  <!-- EN: A strange cube has landed nearby. It shines like gold but is impossible to scratch. It's light and warm to the touch. The way light plays across its surface is captivating.\n\n{PAWN_nameDef} feels inexplicably drawn to the cube.\n\nStudy the cube to learn more about it. -->
  <GoldenCubeArrivalText>一个奇怪的魔方坠落在附近。虽然它像黄金一样闪闪发光，但却质地坚硬，刮不出一点痕迹。它的触感轻盈而温暖。它表面折射出漂亮迷人的光芒。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}感觉自己莫名其妙就被这个魔方给迷住了。\n\n研究这个魔方以了解更多信息。</GoldenCubeArrivalText>

